These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, brazilian, nigerian
1. the colombian is in an odd position##4
2. the nigerian is between the australian and the colombian##2
3. the nigerian is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | australian | nigerian | colombian | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, onion, plum, mango
1. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating onion is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | onion | apple | mango | plum |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, animation, horror, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
2. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching horror movies is between the person watching western movies and the person watching animation movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | western | horror | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, skiing, cycling, tennis
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
2. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | skiing | basketball | tennis | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, snowboarding, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | rugby | snowboarding | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, malaysian, egyptian, indian
1. the malaysian is on the far right##1
2. the malaysian is on the left or right of the indian##3
3. the egyptian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | french | indian | malaysian |

