1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | card-games | board-games | puzzles | magic-tricks |

