.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, train, tram, trike
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the train is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | tram | train | trike | ship |

